  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>These wicked-looking spiked metal wheels fit around the ankles and jingle when the wearer walks, imposing a -1 item penalty on Stealth checks. If used as a weapon, they are treated as a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.YFfG2fMyaIAXkmtr]{Spiked Gauntlet}.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are riding a mount</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You kick both spurs into your mount's flank. Your mount takes @Damage[2d6[bleed]] and gains the quickened condition for 1 minute or until the persistent bleed damage ends, whichever comes first. It can use the extra action only to Stride.</p>"
